snippet.title: Guns and Rush (Aliens Survivor) - Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2065770/

Guns and Rush is a challenging sci-fi rogue-like bullet-hell with rpg elements. Build a new unique character each run and survive 30 minutes against hordes of tens of thousands of aliens! Discover unique weapons, collect powerfull items and level up to become indestructible!
